summary: 2 types of dresses, 1 type of stockings, shoes, bracelets. Few colors.
descriptionHtml:
Mod was made for CBBE 3.4f (latest) body, supports weight slider.
Shoes are craftable in leather, other items are in chest in Riverwood (look screens)
Name begins from "DressS"
Items are light armor and temperable

[size=5]Requires [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/36213]HDT high heels[/url][/size]

2 type of dresses, 1 bracelets, 1 stockings (slot 53), 1 shoes
Few colors of each item (bracelets 1 color)

You can make anything what you want while it is non-commercial destribution and you give me credits as original mod author.
I don't give permission to upload it in steam.

Your screenshots will be greatly appreciated.
